{"tid":1161263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"引渡修例通過不是最差　北韓都是有人住　香港是可以不斷更差","createTime":"2019-05-19T05:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T06:55:48.000Z","uid":47714,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef6adef75f29f03cddadf91144854311931894b","tid":1161263,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1129759162622201858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1129759162622201858&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=0f5ddc27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1129759162622201858&h=0042f5bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1129759162622201858</a><br />\n<br />\n已經不同人講過。香港明天或將會某日不是甚麼最黑暗的一天。北韓都是有人住的。再惡劣下去還是有人住的，不要少看人類的適應力。香港不會最差，只會更差。香港人失去更多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154145206207357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10154145206207357&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=5819123d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154145206207357</a><br />\n<br />\n香港不會死, 就像上海其實也沒有死一樣, 還是有些上海人會爭取上海話的生存, 以及復興上海文化. 只是... 在上海爭取上海的復興, 比在香港維護香港的未來, 要困難很多, 畢竟上海的文化被破壞的程度甚深, 香港還富有很巨大的力量. 我們在這起點開始, 總比別人容易.<br />\n<br />\n也就是說, 如果我們這一代不爭氣. 那麼, 在未來就會有一些人, 也希望復興香港, 但他們將會面臨更惡劣的處境. 無論我們散佈多少失敗主義, 事情還是會繼續的, 不過以後的世代會抱怨我們, 為何不及早行動呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154143720537357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10154143720537357&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=37c9afed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154143720537357</a><br />\n<br />\n今天我們還很強大, 所以我們今天就需要行動, 而不是等事情再惡化之後, 留給後代一個更惡劣的環境要他們面對. 就像污染食水不會令我們立即就滅亡, 但他會留給後代長久的健康損害. 致癌物不會令我們立即就死, 但會令我們未來有大病, 成為社會未來的醫療開支. 所謂短視與有遠見, 分別就在於能否看到未來.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154112592152357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10154112592152357&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=1bfcd744\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154112592152357</a><br />\n<br />\n其實, 那些趨炎附勢的人, 在情況越惡劣的時候, 他們只會越加強其趨炎附勢的傾向, 參考那些每年通漲幾倍的非洲第三世界國家, 他們會因為景況越來越惡劣, 而令政權轉移嗎? 如果你有看, 通常景況越惡劣, 既得利益者和已有的勝利者的權力反而更緊, 支持他們的人反而更為失去理性和偏執. 因為他們知道, 自己已經趨炎附勢那麼久, 根本已無法轉向, 如果失去政權會大禍臨頭.<br />\n<br />\n除非有外國的援助, 否則難以引爆革命, 因為長期社會就只有兩種人, 一種是親政府的人, 剩下的全是烏合之眾, 欠缺組織與信任是難以引爆革命的. 外國的援助與其說是給軍火, 給錢, 不如說是透過外交和團結的方法, 將他們組織起來, 建立互信.<br />\n<br />\n如果沒有革命, 那社會會走向安康嗎? 不會, 沒有革命, 社會會走向退化, 更走向階級化, 封建社會, 種姓制度, 甚至是退化回一個家族部落."},{"pid":"4613b12333dbda61171acab09e6b6262632f6203","tid":1161263,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:26:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8fd18247008aa29464fad7c18c5747ed6dd1650a","tid":1161263,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44859faba0599bf3c633a4a6d90c7d6a9f772050","tid":1161263,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77176f38643b6141580842a597e92310524582c6","tid":1161263,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"起來 不願做奴隸的人們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a234201063b50555ae7687d686abb3bef77169","tid":1161263,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"鄭立真係好勁"},{"pid":"b95f7dfabf6af68fba06b571b8ee0af169fe806f","tid":1161263,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"要科幾多水？"}]}